  "body": "**Description**\r\nRerunning at the restart should run only 64 last blocks but instead of that on few of my long running nodes it is reprocessing thousands of them. Here is a log from my Gnosis node:\r\n<img width=\"313\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/NethermindEth/nethermind/assets/43241881/c48d3e3c-f93e-4508-b098-b6d268a5fbf8\">\r\nThe only problem which it gaves me is a bit bigger downtime of a node + during that time we are not processing current blocks so we can lose a bit more of the validator rewards.\r\n",
